<br>
Sameth the Infiltrator <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usanlaildsnayel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sanlail DSnayel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/30/02 11:45:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3849.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Just to be fair</span><hr size=1> Yes we Nightshades could respec to slashing weapons.  Of course we suck at slashing because of our low strength so you have to subtract the difference there.<br>
