<br>
W/o a buff bot, i would 120 these same people.<br>
<br>
Balance is skewed when people are sickly buffed, even by a low 40's bot.<br>
<br>
Last LA sb i fought was mainhanding me for 101, and offhanding me for 35 (she was level 50 also).  Didnt drop any buffs upon death... I was buff botted (see my buff bot experiment post a while back, normally dont bot but this night i happened to want to try it out) by a 46 enhance cleric, and was mainhanding for 270-290 / offhanding for 80-101.  SB are pretty weak now unbuffed, the reason they can hit hard with a buff bot is most likely due to the high cap of doublefrost? (was the cap or base nerfed), which they would never be able to reach normally, or even moderately buffed.<br>
<br>
